Package in.ac.iitk.cse.putwb.ui.actions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Action
    An abstract class for creating content that can be shown in an ActionPanel
    AnalyzeAction
    The Results and Analysis action provides user with the results of a successfully completed experiment.
    AttributeFilterAction
    Attribute filtering action allows users to select a set of attributes to mask from the results being displayed inside a results and analysis action.
    RunAction
    The Execution Action executes starts a PUTExperiment based on the user preferences.
    SelectClassifierAction
    The Classifier Selection action allows user to choose a particular (weka) classifier for classification, and provide any custom options, if required.
    SelectPrivacySettingsAction
    This action takes inputs that are central to the working of the experiment.
    SetExpenseAction
    This action allows user to curtail the computational expense of the experiment, by setting values for horizontal and vertical expenses.
    UploadFileAction
    The dataset selection action allows user to select or reset a dataset to use for the experiment
